## DESIGN PATTERNS

### Section Compactness
- Use Cases / FAQ → accordion (not card grid)
- "Blind Spot" problem sections → horizontal strip with icons + 1-line descriptions
- Partnership / How It Works → short descriptions (1-2 lines max)
- Portfolio Scale → horizontal strip (left title + right checklist)

### CTA Sections
- Final CTA → blue gradient container (`#4A7FB3 → #365f8a`), white text, radial glow
- Primary button: glassmorphism white on gradient (`rgba(255,255,255,0.15)` + backdrop-blur)
- Ghost button: transparent + white border

### Footer
All customer-facing pages: branded footer with logo + Industries + Resources links + copyright.
Footer links: Developers & Agents, Automotive, NFC Cards | Live Demo, Contact Sales, Log in

### Modal Accessibility
- `role="dialog"` + `aria-modal="true"` on backdrop
- `aria-labelledby` pointing to modal title id
- Close button: `aria-label="Close"`
- Required fields: `aria-required="true"`
- Error display: inline (never `alert()`)

### Animations
- Glass morphism: `backdrop-filter: blur(12px)` on cards
- Particle effects: floating dots for ambient depth
- NFC wave pulse on hero elements
- Staggered card entry: `fadeInUp` with 0.05s delays
- Card flip: 3D perspective (`perspective: 1000px`)
- Scroll reveal: IntersectionObserver with `.ent-reveal` / `.hp-reveal` classes
- How It Works icons: CSS keyframe animations (VIP=checkmark draw, Delivery=lid open, Tap=ripple, Intelligence=bar rise)
- ROI icon: animated 3-color bars (mint #A8D5BA, blue #6FA8DC, dark #365f8a)
- Always wrap in `@media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) { ... }`

### Popup Timing
```
CookieConsent:     8s
WhatsApp tooltip: 20s
PushNotification: 45s
EmailCapture:    300s (5 minutes) — hidden on demo URLs
```

