## GIT CONVENTIONS

- Branch naming: `feat/feature-name`, `fix/bug-name`, `refactor/area`
- Commit messages: imperative mood, max 72 chars
  - `feat: add pipeline kanban to CRM dashboard`
  - `fix: newsletter popup appearing on demo URLs`
  - `refactor: split AutoDashboard into sub-components`
- Never commit `node_modules/`, `.firebase/`, `dist/`, `.env`

