## FILE STRUCTURE

```
frontend/src/
  App.jsx                          # All routes + lazy loading
  firebase.js                      # Firebase config (auth, db exports)
  main.jsx                         # Entry point
  contexts/AuthContext.jsx          # Auth provider
  hooks/useAdmin.js                # Admin check
  hooks/useTracking.js             # BroadcastChannel tracking (demo)
  services/firestoreTracking.js    # Firestore tracking (production)
  i18n/
    index.js                       # registerTranslations + useTranslation
    common.js                      # Shared translations
    pages/                         # Per-page translation modules (9 files)
    portals/                       # Per-portal translation modules (5 files)
  config/developerThemes.js        # Multi-developer theming (tower data, units, labels)
  styles/ent-base.css              # Shared Enterprise/Developers/RealEstate base
  components/
    Navbar/Navbar.jsx              # Global navbar
    IndustriesDropdown.jsx         # Industries mega menu
    EmailCapture/EmailCapture.jsx  # Newsletter popup (5min delay)
    WhatsAppButton/                # WhatsApp floating button
    CookieConsent/                 # GDPR cookie banner
    SEO/                           # Meta tags component
    ProtectedRoute/                # Auth guard wrapper
  pages/
    Home/Home.jsx + Home.css
    CRMGateway/CRMGateway.jsx+css  # Demo entry — industry selector
    Developers/Developers.jsx+css   # RE Developers & Agents
    Enterprise/Enterprise.jsx       # Multi-industry sales page
    NFCCards/NFCCards.jsx           # NFC card products
    Automotive/Automotive.jsx       # Auto industry page
    VIPPortal/                      # Khalid Al-Rashid (self-contained)
    AhmedPortal/                    # Ahmed Al-Fahad (self-contained)
    MarketplacePortal/              # Public marketplace (self-contained)
    Dashboard/                      # CRM analytics dashboard
    AutomotiveDemo/                 # 6 auto demo components
    Admin/tabs/                     # 8 admin tab components
    ROICalculator/                  # Sales ROI tool
    CardRedirect/                   # NFC tap handler (client-side fallback)
functions/
  index.js                          # Cloud Functions (cardRedirect, API, Wallet)
  package.json
```

